Interface RequestParameters

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AssociationParams, CorpNotesParams, EntityParams, FastFindParams, FileParams, MetaParams, QueryParams, ResumeFileParseParams, ResumeTextParseParams, SearchParams
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    StandardAssociationParams, StandardCorpNotesParams, StandardEntityParams, StandardFileParams, StandardMetaParams, StandardQueryParams, StandardResumeFileParseParams, StandardResumeTextParseParams, StandardSearchParams

    public interface RequestParameters
    Represents a type of parameter used for api calls.
    Author:
    magnus.palm

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Map<String,String> getParameterMap()
      Returns parameters needed for this particular api call.
      String getUrlString()
      Returns a url String in the format &fieldName1={fieldName1}&fieldName2={fieldName2}.

    • Method Detail

      • getUrlString

        String getUrlString()
        Returns a url String in the format &fieldName1={fieldName1}&fieldName2={fieldName2}. Fields that are null will not be included in the url string.
        Returns:

      • getParameterMap

        Map<String,String> getParameterMap()
        Returns parameters needed for this particular api call. Adds the parameters to a map in format key:value = fieldName:fieldValue and returns that map.
        Returns:
